snippet.title: 3D Space-Wars - ZX Spectrum [Longplay]
snippet.description:
What do you think of 3D Space-Wars?
This is a longplay of the console version which was released in 1983.
The video will show a full walkthrough and display the gameplay.

Did you play this game or have any opinion on what you can see?
Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

Completion Criteria: Complete each level (each level has a different enemy type until they repeat)

Developed by: Steve Turner
Published by: Hewson Consultants Ltd
Played by: Gremolin
